To run: ./play.py

Portability: you're on your own, sorry :-/

Installation: (assuming you're lucky) 
	make
	edit *.py to reflect where python is kept on your system
	./play.py

	you must be in this directory, to read the dictionary (min.42k)
	and the bitmaps (./bitmap/*)

License:  do whatever you want to/with this stuff, just don't make
any money out of it, and I'd appreciate it if you send me any diffs.

Gameplay: drag a line to indicate roughly where you want to place a
word, type the word and hit return.
